author: Reuters
title: New US projections show summer coronavirus infection spike if restrictions are lifted, report says
description: New U.S. government figures show coronavirus infections will spike during the summer if stay-at-home orders are lifted after 30 days as planned, the New York Times reported on Friday.
content:
